-- Chennai Gets Third Water Desalination Plant, Times of India Says
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2013-04-16T13:42:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-16/chennai-gets-third-water-desalination-plant-times-of-india-says.html
Chennai will get a third
desalination plant to meet growing demands for water in the
southern Indian city, the Times of  India  reported, citing chief
minister J Jayalalithaa.  The new treated water facility in Nemmeli is part of civic
drinking water improvements and road infrastructure upgrades
valued at about $317 million, the minister told the state
assembly, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
